snippet.title: Best VGM 856 - VVVVVV - Potential for Anything
snippet.description:
Get the game's album here: http://www.souleye.se/

See also:
Best VGM 709 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E99qxCMb05g
Best VGM 1186 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0dMkx7c-uNM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / 3DS
VVVVVV (2010)
Potential for Anything
Magnus Palsson
